title.rendered: Britney Spears to Ex-Husband, Tabloids: Y’all Can Kiss My A$$!

content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

Reports that Britney Spears was physically abused by Jason Trawick shocked the Hollywood world this week, but have been adamantly denied by her camp.

Now the singer herself has gone on record with a Tweet for the axis of evil – Star Magazine, Radar Online and Jason Alexander – who fabricated the tale.

Pucker up, jerks, and kiss her … well, see below.

Brit also says she has a new album coming out and is “off on a romantic weekend” with Trawick for her birthday. Guess it’s clear where she stands!
